Thank you, Jacob 😎

Looking at the HTML, it seems like `object-tools` has been moved to a more appropriate location (outside of content rather than inside).

I think we need to remove some attributes that were added in the previous PR.

<img width="957" height="179" alt="Image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/8c4ebbcc-2496-4a57-85ed-b3653ecd0454" />

When the title is long, `object-tools` gets cut off. It seems to be caused by overflow: hidden.
```diff --git a/django/contrib/admin/static/admin/css/base.css b/django/contrib/admin/static/admin/css/base.css
index ed5791a6eb..e6ddfc11a2 100644
--- a/django/contrib/admin/static/admin/css/base.css
+++ b/django/contrib/admin/static/admin/css/base.css
@@ -839,7 +839,6 @@ a.deletelink:focus, a.deletelink:hover {

 .object-tools {
     padding: 0;
-    overflow: hidden;
     text-align: right;
     margin: 0 0 15px;
 }
```

I don't think these two are needed anymore either.

```diff --git a/django/contrib/admin/static/admin/css/base.css b/django/contrib/admin/static/admin/css/base.css
index ed5791a6eb..257663b7c8 100644
--- a/django/contrib/admin/static/admin/css/base.css
+++ b/django/contrib/admin/static/admin/css/base.css
@@ -839,14 +839,11 @@ a.deletelink:focus, a.deletelink:hover {

 .object-tools {
     padding: 0;
     overflow: hidden;
-    text-align: right;
     margin: 0 0 15px;
 }

 .object-tools li {
     display: inline-block;
-    height: auto;
 }

```

<img width="403" height="173" alt="Image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/b3255f64-9c89-470e-82f8-5f7aa958eacf" />

Previously, on mobile screens, `object-tools` occupied a single line.
I'm not sure if this was an intentional change.

Thanks Jacob 
There are a lot of regressions happening with this work 😢
Additionally, I found one `CSS` thing that should have been done before.
```diff --git a/django/contrib/admin/static/admin/css/forms.css b/django/contrib/admin/static/admin/css/forms.css
index e3b7d58857..6294f368b6 100644
--- a/django/contrib/admin/static/admin/css/forms.css
+++ b/django/contrib/admin/static/admin/css/forms.css
@@ -30,7 +30,8 @@ form .form-row p {
     flex-wrap: wrap;
 }
 
-.form-multiline > div {
+.form-multiline > div,
+.form-multiline > fieldset {
     padding-bottom: 10px;
 }
```

